This is supported:
```scala
scala> val f: (Boolean, => Int) => Int = (b, i) => if (b) i else 0
f: (Boolean, => Int) => Int = <function2>

scala> f(false, ???)
res0: Int = 0

scala> f(true, ???)
scala.NotImplementedError: an implementation is missing
  at scala.Predef$.$qmark$qmark$qmark(Predef.scala:225)
```

